title: John Stossel - Why Free Trade Is Better Than "Made In America"!
description:
This short comes from John Stossels show on Fox Business Network where he sits down with economist Art Carden and talks about the myths about "made in america" and how free trade is better not only for countries who we outsource the labor to, but for our country as well.

"The fundamental thing about trade, it makes everybody better off." - Art Carden, Economist from Samford University
